{"tid":2511354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地藝術家偷197件女性內衣褲創作《197》？　入選中國SAP藝術大獎惹爭議","createTime":"2021-05-01T00:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T00:58:13.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c211203a6c526f02dbd5bb68ce5fed0f751357","tid":2511354,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S9sUaZlWRjGNll872_OEivGAjnA=/802x560/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQEPQ3C4PRFQ5ETQ7Z4KVL2XBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS9sUaZlWRjGNll872_OEivGAjnA%3D%2F802x560%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQEPQ3C4PRFQ5ETQ7Z4KVL2XBM.jpg&h=40558b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參賽作品《197》的作者張明信自爆偷197件內衣褲做素材，引發爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3wUrBsDOgGhJux-wxV8ViIkmlxc=/802x542/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I4DWB7DSX5DYTAQGEIGEZETIMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3wUrBsDOgGhJux-wxV8ViIkmlxc%3D%2F802x542%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI4DWB7DSX5DYTAQGEIGEZETIMA.jpg&h=4d0fa6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張明信發佈拍有偷竊過程的47秒影片。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n內地藝術家張明信參加ARTCLOUD中國SAP（The Signature Art Prize China）藝術大獎，其作品《197》成功入圍，未料他在「創作說明」中竟寫道，這是他兩年內以「非正常方式」獲取197件女性內衣褲作為「展品」呈現，還附上一段盜竊過程影片。有民眾發現後爆料給媒體並報警，輿論令主辦方隨即取消其參賽資格，並下架作品。不過，北京警方昨（4月30日）通報指，這些內衣褲是張男買來的，但他虛構是盜竊所得，已對他採取刑事強制措施。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，SAP藝術大獎於2006年於英國創辦，專為表彰中青年藝術家領域的藝術獎項。ARTCLOUD中國SAP藝術大獎由ARTCLOUD獨立營運，同時是中國首個國際青年藝術家獎項。<br />\n北京一名沈姓女子日前為這項藝術大獎投票時，赫然發現作品《197》的作者張明信自爆，作品是以他在2018年至2020年間偷來的197件內衣褲作為素材，還附上47秒長的盜竊過程影片。她隨即於4月26日聯絡組委會，要求主辦方撤掉作品，並嚴肅跟進事件。沈女更在網上公開事件，同時向北京市公安局舉報，警方隨後聯絡她表示正在調查。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210501/QTMNPK4A35FA7M3ABHGL5TJV4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210501%2FQTMNPK4A35FA7M3ABHGL5TJV4Q%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4a8f43fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210501%2FQTMNPK4A35FA7M3ABHGL5TJV4Q%2F&h=154ca8af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210501/QTMNPK4A35FA7M3ABHGL5TJV4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"0c5602674c642c372cc58e82c9606cd6705aaaab","tid":2511354,"uid":271835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:41:35.000Z","msg":"啲bra堆埋一齊邊度藝術&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d59c557d99667c695b36f6f6ad536564de546a2","tid":2511354,"uid":290985,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0c5602674c642c372cc58e82c9606cd6705aaaab","tid":2511354,"uid":271835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:41:35.000Z","msg":"啲bra堆埋一齊邊度藝術&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:43:15.000Z","msg":"代表住中國優良傳統文化<br />\n偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"fee9d91400bfcde16a15d5617edefed100c2c7d1","tid":2511354,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e48f3503f6a64f7b092ffc378700aa662132808","tid":2511354,"uid":179422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:53:28.000Z","msg":"咁似深水埗廿蚊個任揀嗰啲bra"},{"pid":"07d637d066c86c9f726f703cd61f0dae70c8f815","tid":2511354,"uid":24270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5602674c642c372cc58e82c9606cd6705aaaab","tid":2511354,"uid":271835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:41:35.000Z","msg":"啲bra堆埋一齊邊度藝術&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />